{"tid":1145737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國商務部:美國若升級貿戰 中國將不得不反制","createTime":"2019-05-08T22:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T04:13:19.000Z","uid":41404,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"13d47e229bd773daf067cbe87f571d175b8b6e1f","tid":1145737,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T22:27:40.000Z","msg":"美國政府擬於本周五(5月10日)凌晨起，將2000億美元中國輸美商品的關稅從10%上調至25%。中國商務部在其網站上發表聲明，稱升級貿易摩擦不符合兩國人民和世界人民的利益，中方對此深表遺憾；如果美方關稅措施付諸實施，中方將不得不採取必要反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普上周日突然在社交媒體Twitter貼文，揚言本周五對華2000億美元貨品調高關稅至25%，其他未加徵關稅的3250億美元中國貨，短期內亦會徵收25%關稅。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周三再在Twitter貼文指出，接獲中國通知，國務院副總理劉鶴正前往美國，冀與華府磋商並達成貿易協議。特朗普又稱，很滿意每年超過1000億美元的關稅來填補美國國庫，對美國而言是好事，相反，對中國則不利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2132837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2132837&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyftKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=436d49d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2132837</a>"},{"pid":"76c17ae7937c699721988b3b0a30bc1ece1f8765","tid":1145737,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T23:24:56.000Z","msg":"支爆啦 , 頂到幾多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4df1824354a1bb43c250105417b8a143304a6f","tid":1145737,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T23:26:37.000Z","msg":"總之中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f826eabdb7dfd14f6cc774ac1e04338f6ac0d31a","tid":1145737,"uid":61280,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T23:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/09/072932_a2554c